---
import BaseLayout from '@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro'
import siteConfig from '@/site-config'
---

<BaseLayout description={siteConfig.description}>
  <article class="prose">
    <h1 class="text-title">👋 Hello, there! I'm Alif Nuryana</h1>
    <p>Welcome to my personal space on the web.</p>
    <p>
      I'm a software engineer with a passion for coding, problem-solving, and
      continuous learning. This site is a reflection of my journey in the tech
      world, where I share my insights, experiences, and projects that have
      shaped my career and growth.
    </p>
    <p>
      Here, you’ll find a collection of blogs, notes, talks, and projects that
      I’ve worked on. My goal is to provide insights and share experiences to
      support others in their learning journeys while fostering a community
      focused on growth and innovation.
    </p>
    <p>Explore the following highlights:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>📝 In-depth blogs on software engineering topics</li>
      <li>📚 Technical notes and guides</li>
      <li>🎤 Recordings and slides from talks I've given</li>
      <li>💻 Projects that showcase my coding journey</li>
    </ul>
    <p>
      Whether you're here to learn, collaborate, or just explore, I hope you
      find something valuable. Feel free to reach out if you have questions or
      want to connect.
    </p>
    <p>
      Check out my
      <a target="_blank" href="https://github.com/alifnuryana">GitHub</a>
      to see my open-source contributions, or follow me on
      <a target="_blank" href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/alifn27">LinkedIn</a>
      to stay updated with my latest work.
    </p>
    <hr class="hr-line" />
    <p>Connect with me on</p>
    <p class="flex gap-x-4 gap-y-2 flex-wrap">
      {
        siteConfig.socialLinks.map((link) => (
          <a
            aria-label={link.text}
            href={link.href}
            target="_blank"
            class="prose-link"
          >
            <i class:list={[link.icon]} />
            {link.text}
          </a>
        ))
      }
    </p>
    <p>
      Have questions or just want to chat? Feel free to drop me an email at
      <a
        prose-link
        aria-label={siteConfig.email}
        href={`mailto:${siteConfig.email}`}
      >
        {siteConfig.email}
      </a>.
    </p>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
